ial\">factorial</a></span>)</span><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inv.inv\">⁻¹</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSMul.hSMul\">•</a> <span class=\"fn\">x</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HPow.hPow\">^</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Algebra/Exponential.html#NormedSpace.expSeries_apply_eq'","kind":"theorem","line":137,"name":"NormedSpace.expSeries_apply_eq'","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Algebra/Exponential.lean#L137-L139"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Algebra/Exponential.html#NormedSpace.expSeries_apply_eq\"><span class=\"name\">NormedSpace</span>.<span class=\"name\">expSeries_apply_eq</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝕂</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Field/Defs.html#Field\">Field</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕂</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Ring/Defs.html#Ring\">Ring</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Defs.html#Algebra\">Algebra</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕂</span> <span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\