decl_kind\">noncomputable def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Algebra/Exponential.html#NormedSpace.exp\"><span class=\"name\">NormedSpace</span>.<span class=\"name\">exp</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_3}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Ring/Defs.html#Ring\">Ring</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Basic.html#TopologicalSpace\">TopologicalSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/Ring/Basic.html#IsTopologicalRing\">IsTopologicalRing</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`NormedSpace.exp : 𝔸 → 𝔸` is the exponential map. It is defined as the sum of the\n`FormalMultilinearSeries` `expSeries ℚ 𝔸`.\n\nIf `𝔸` can't be equipped with a `ℚ`-algebra structure, we use the junk value `1`. For details on why\nthis approach is taken, see the module documentation for\n`Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Algebra/Exponential.lean`.\n\nNote that when `𝔸 = Matrix n n 𝕂`, this is the **Matrix Exponential**; see\n`Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Algebra/MatrixExponential.lean` for lemmas\nspecific to that case. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Algebra/Exponential.html#NormedSpace.exp","kind":"def","line":117,"name":"NormedSpace.exp","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Algebra/Exponential.lean#L117-L132"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Algebra/Exponential.html#NormedSpace.exp_def\"><span class=\"name\">NormedSpace</span>.<span class=\"name\">exp_def</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_3}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Ring/Defs.html#Ring\">Ring</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Basic.html#TopologicalSpace\">TopologicalSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/Ring/Basic.html#IsTopologicalRing\">IsTopologicalRing</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Algebra/Exponential.html#NormedSpace.exp\">exp</a> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">if h : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nonempty\">Nonempty</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Defs.html#Algebra\">Algebra</a> <a href=\"./Init/Data/Rat/Basic.html#Rat\">ℚ</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span>)</span></span> then <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Algebra/Exponential.html#NormedSpace.expSeries\">expSeries</a> <a href=\"./Init/Data/Rat/Basic.html#Rat\">ℚ</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span>)</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Analytic/ConvergenceRadius.html#FormalMultilinearSeries.sum\">sum</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span> else <span class=\"fn\">1</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Algebra/Exponential.html#NormedSpace.exp_def","kind":"theorem","line":117,"name":"NormedSpace.exp_def","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Algebra/Exponential.lean#L117-L132"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Algebra/Exponential.html#NormedSpace.expSeries_eq_ofScalars\"><span class=\"name\">NormedSpace</span>.<span class=\"name\">expSeries_eq_ofScalars</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">𝕂</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Field/Defs.html#Field\">Field</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕂</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Ring/Defs.html#Ring\">Ring</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Defs.html#Algebra\">Algebra</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕂</span> <span class=\"fn\">𝔸</span></spa